      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard that mirrors its original factory delivery. The vehicle exhibits an impeccable exterior luster paired with a flawless, smoke-free interior, signaling a history of meticulous stewardship. Every mechanical system has been vetted for peak performance, ensuring this remains a definitive choice for the sophisticated buyer who demands excellence without exception. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in pristine, showroom condition.",
      "price": 48900.0,
